i like the belly-button lint / eggshell case idea the best, if you're
feeling particularly industrious some eventful evening. or you can
do what i did one soggy summer: open the fuel line, drain some onto a piece of rough or rotten wood, stick that into the middle of the soon-to-
be inferno and carefully strike a match... as kurt vonnegut titled one
of the latter chapters in cat's cradle, "ah-whoom!" works like a charm every time :-) /-----b-o-d-y---i-s---t-h-e---b-i-k-e----------------------------\
